Detailed explanation of generator features in:

John Campbell, R. Keith Ellis, Paolo Nason, Emanuele Re,
Dec 4, 2014. : arXiv:1412.1828

Look at the test-lhc or test-parallel-lhc for sample setups.

Do:

$ make pwhg_main
$ pwhg_main

to generate events.

$ make main-PYTHIA8-lhef

to shower and analyze events.
